John Nugent-Hayward https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Nugent-Hayward 0 John Nugent-Hayward, real name Harold Newton, was an Australian actor with extensive experience in films and radio. He was born and raised in England before moving to Australia. He became one of the best known radio actors in the country.
